<h3>Vision</h3>
<p><%= t('general.company') %>’s vision is to provide people with impaired mobility, their families, and caregivers with a pre-eminent online destination for education and community, anchored by best-in-class video content on coping with daily mobility challenges. This authoritative, relevant content is the core of a community whereby individuals with mobility impairment, their families, and caregivers can connect with others, share information and resources, and gain strength and education to allow them to meet and surmount the daily challenges of living with disability.</p>

