  <li><strong>Best-in-class “one stop shopping” content,</strong> informed by our leadership team’s personal and professional experiences with the challenges of impaired mobility</li>
  <li><strong>Deep relationships</strong> and brand-enhancing partnerships with multiple leading advocacy groups in the disability and mobility spaces</li>
  <li><strong>Diversified business model with broad commercial reach</strong>  that leverages the same content across relevant markets to generate revenues simultaneously from consumers, health care facilities, and major corporations</li>
